~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : pemote                                    ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : pemote <username> <message>

   This allows you to do private emotes to individual users. 
   The '/' sign can be used as a shortcut.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : emote, shemote
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
